## Secretary's report

Jonathan reported there had been a couple of emails from projects
interested in becoming associated with SPI, and both had been replied to.
There was also an outstanding request from sidux, which Ferdinand (devil)
informed us was no longer valid.

## Outstanding minutes

There were no outstanding minutes available for voting upon.

## Any other business

Joshua asked if the rest of the board would consider Cyanogen and K9
Mail (both Android related projects) as suitable candidates for associated
project status. There were no objections to him contacting them.

## Adjournment

The meeting was adjourned until Wednesday, October 13th, 2010 at 20:00
UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.

